Path Recruitment Message 6

Date: 02/07/2023

Good morrow, scientists of the lab!

It is now the 6th day of our recruitment drive, and we, The Path, wouldst like to extend a warm invitation to thee.

We are a team of mutated apes, proud and strong, and we believe that our mutations maketh us the best of all.

To join our ranks is a reward in itself, for with us, thou shalt be part of a noble cause, one that will forever be remembered in the annals of history.

So, come forth and be counted among us, for the journey ahead shall be both glorious and fulfilling.

We await your swift reply, good sirs and madams.

Together, we are unstoppable.

Join us and be a part of The Path.
